relatedResults.title: Game Of Thrones
relatedResults.description: Several royal families desire the Iron Throne to gain control of Westeros. Whilst kingdoms fight each other for power, a sinister force lurks beyond the Wall in the north.

relatedResults.title: How I Met Your Mother
relatedResults.description: It is the story of Ted and how he fell in love. It all started when Ted’s best friend, Marshall, drops the bombshell that he’s going to propose to his long-time girlfriend, Lily, a kindergarten teacher.

relatedResults.title: True Blood
relatedResults.description: Vampires not only exist, but the entire world knows about them. Since a Japanese scientist's invention of synthetic blood, vampires have progressed from legendary monsters to fellow citizens overnight.

relatedResults.title: American Horror Story
relatedResults.description: A family of three who have moved from Boston to LA for a fresh start but end up living in a sinister haunted house instead.
